	IDENTIFICATION DIVISION.
	PROGRAM-ID. FIBONACCI.
	AUTHOR. EVELYN.

	DATA DIVISION.
	WORKING-STORAGE SECTION.
	01 WS-TARGET	PIC 9(10).
	01 WS-SOLUTION	PIC 9(10).

	PROCEDURE DIVISION.
	DISPLAY "ENTER FIBONACCI TARGET: ".
	ACCEPT WS-TARGET.

	CALL "RECURSION" USING WS-TARGET WS-SOLUTION.

	DISPLAY "THE TARGET FIBONACCI NUMBER IS " WS-SOLUTION.
	STOP RUN.
	END PROGRAM FIBONACCI.

